                    </a>
                </h3>
                                                                                            <div class="image column__banner">
                    <a href="https://www-develop.yogananda.org/de/self-realization-fellowship" title="Die Mission der Self-Realization Fellowship" class="uprise" id="nav_about_mission_image_click">
                        <img src="https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/yogananda-dev/SRF-B-Chidananda-DSC07096-01-250x219-px_2021-12-08-183229_inrf.jpg" alt="">
